There are 2 types of house orientation available. The infomation of these house orientations are listed as follows:
(S)South orientation: The north and south are well ventilated, with sufficient lighting, and have the characteristics of warm winter and cool summer;

(N)North orientation: This orientation has poor lighting, with no sunlight throughout the year.However, in summer, it feels cooler, while in winter, it becomes colder. Over time, the room's Yin Qi becomes heavier, which is not very good for physical health;
